_sText:
(Update: Reupdated file due to lacking a file + reupdated screenies!) and so on + sorry for late entry.

This is my entry for The Christmas Triple-Design Contest, I went for a victorian style setting! I decided to go with a prefab pack of a few things;
Content:
A Tower, A Cabin, A Bridge, A Hut, Base of the tower

I intended to make a better showcase map but this was thrown together in the space of two minutes about 3 minutes to midnight!  So it is what it is!  The content is good though so try it out!  

Note I: Please Credit me on release of your map if you use one of my prefabs, (Terrora).

Note II: If you have any suggestions for future prefabs please tell me! And I will do my best to make it for you asap!

Thanks Alex (Terrora / Roluffy)
